<pre class="highlightjs highlight"><code class="language-bash hljs" data-lang="bash">$ curl 'http://localhost:9393/jobs/executions?name=DOCJOB&amp;page=0&amp;size=10' -i -X GET</code></pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
